<div id="post-333972" class="blog-post position-11 odd-post"><div class="odd-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/libreoffice/blog/marketing-conference-call-for-june">Marketing Conference Call for June</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">13 de Junho de 2011, 0:00</span><span class="author">, por Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/libreoffice/blog/marketing-conference-call-for-june#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>sem comentários ainda</span></a></span></span><p>Marketing Conference Call for June will be on Wednesday, the 22nd, at 1500 UTC. More details are <a href="http://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Marketing/ConfCalls">available in the wiki</a>.</p>
<br>  <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/facebook/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gotwitter/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/twitter/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/stumble/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godigg/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/digg/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/" border="0" alt=""></a> <a href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/goreddit/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/"><img src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/reddit/tdfsc.wordpress.com/528/" border="0" alt=""></a> <img src="http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=blog.documentfoundation.org&amp;blog=17531842&amp;post=528&amp;subd=tdfsc&amp;ref=&amp;feed=1" border="0" height="1" alt="" width="1"><br style="clear:both"/></div></div>
